{"tid":1668922,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"轉Note10+ 定 ROG phone 2 好","createTime":"2019-10-22T09:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T02:46:53.000Z","uid":227581,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"af789420bd5aba3144fc822825d676fd56a77da9","tid":1668922,"uid":227581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"事關對於Apple近年都係無咩創意<br />\n想轉An機搞搞新意思<br />\n<br />\n好多人都話打機就ROG 日常生活+商務就N10+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我兩種需求都有 點選擇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nROG = <br />\n120hz mon<br />\n舊電大啲, 個外表又型, 本身電腦都係ROG信仰<br />\n用手制好岩出手汗既人 唔怕誤觸<br />\n音響比較出色<br />\n<br />\nN10+ :<br />\n2K mon <br />\n外表穩重啲 番工果陣拎出黎比較合適<br />\n可以用typeC駁電腦 用Window去control電話 (有時扮工可以偷偷地開遊戲玩)<br />\n<br />\n本身自己係傾向N10+ 始終可以兼容打機 又可以番工<br />\n但係平時電腦都係用144, 用番60hz既mon真係慢到癲<br />\n唔知各位會唔會有其他選擇 (唔諗大陸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"db0fcd96041b363004ddb4257d173251a06b6084","tid":1668922,"uid":23162,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"碌10啦，超聲波指紋好方便，係人都開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898e1c35a319d1f9ecbab46cac26ed77cc8ae4b4","tid":1668922,"uid":42949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"6d47317130b93bb7dbd4f00886571793a10bd3fd","tid":1668922,"uid":227581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0fcd96041b363004ddb4257d173251a06b6084","tid":1668922,"uid":23162,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"碌10啦，超聲波指紋好方便，係人都開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"部手機留低左係屋企 又要用payme 可以搵老豆解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b88f8a08e75a26cea90d92d764e4dee28b2c6ca","tid":1